---
title: Tandoori Chicken & Garlic Rice with Cucumber-Mint Yoghurt & Mango Chutney
description: Enjoy the mild, aromatic flavours of India in a meal that everyone will love! Tender strips of chicken get a light tandoori coating, which goes perfectly with fragrant garlic rice. Finish it off with a creamy mint yoghurt to cover all your bases.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-tikka-garlic-rice-3e6f73ce.jpg
